content:
 Sun by warmth causes traveler to remove
coat, while wind by violent blowing causes him to pull it closer around him.
Wienert FFC LVI 43 (ET 7), 80 (ET 457), 136 (ST 419); Halm Aesop No. 82;
Lithuanian: Balys Index No. 3900; Estonian: Loorits Grundzüge I 381ff.;
Russian: Andrejev No. 298*; Indonesia: DeVries‘s
list Nos. 95, 140. Cf. Halm No. 414.
